AR-006/proposal.md:\n  Line 68: | `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/` | 新增 | `sandbox_delete.go`、`sandbox_delete_test.go` 等 handler 实现文件 |\n  Line 80: | CLI 工具 | 为用户提供 `agentcube sandbox delete <sessionId>` 命令 |\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/sandbox-orchestration/spec.md:\n  Line 126: The system SHALL call `StoreSandbox` with a placeholder `SandboxInfo` before creating the `Sandbox` or `SandboxClaim` in the API; SHALL register a one-shot watcher before create; SHALL wait up to 2 minutes for sandbox status `running` from the reconciler; SHALL resolve pod IP and then `UpdateSandbox` with full info; and SHALL roll back the created CR on failure after the wait (delete Sandbox or SandboxClaim within a 30s timeout context).\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/deployment/design.md:\n  Line 104: | `agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxes` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` |\n  Line 105: | `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxclaims` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` |\n  Line 106: | `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxtemplates` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` |\n  Line 107: | `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io` | `sandboxwarmpools` | `get,list,watch,create,update,patch,delete` |\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/idle-cleanup/spec.md:\n  Line 22: - **THEN** the sandbox is not deleted and result has zero `RequeueAfter`\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cli-toolkit/design.md:\n  Line 52:     \"\"\"AgentCube CLI - A developer tool for AI agent lifecycle management.\"\"\"","metadata":{"matches":17,"truncated":false},"title":"sandbox.*delet|lifecycle.*manag","time":{"start":1775820172259,"end":1775820172270}}}}
